The paper is about scene text detection and recognition using deep learning, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of deep learning also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of different models and benchmarks, which relates to information retrieval (cs.IR).
